{"tid":1041613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★賀！蘋果公司裁員？信件中確定 190 名蘋果職員受影響！","createTime":"2019-03-01T03:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T07:52:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5588e8c3df74b4fff1cd02805ea9661ba9e1ebe1","tid":1041613,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:11:53.000Z","msg":"蘋果在發給加州就業發展局一封信中透露，表示公司將裁員190 人，這部分員工曾在自動駕駛汽車部門工作。受影響的員工包括38 名工程項目經理，33 名硬件工程師、31 名產品設計工程師和22 名軟件工程師，將會在 4 月 16 日生效。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果甚少有裁員的消息，雖然不是全數解僱，一部分職員將被調往公司的其他部門，但代表目前蘋果公司有兩個最大的可能性而作出這個決定，一是智能電動車市場前景不佳，二是蘋果公司在主要收入手機部門上面對困境，要集中資源應付未來的改變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/01/apple-cut-car/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F03%2F01%2Fapple-cut-car%2F&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=fb7fc3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/03/01/apple-cut-car/</a>"},{"pid":"0e0a0f61e48685822bb1972e7e0c355d0fad8fdb","tid":1041613,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"步向死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de8eb3b1acc03d36f74521c80d4e85a211629db","tid":1041613,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f995fc48d658fd310843ae5b8d2c10514968d3b","tid":1041613,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"